\r\n前二項之未遂犯罰之。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/PCDM/111%2c%e7%b0%a1%2c2558%2c20220803%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"PCDM,111,簡,2558,20220803,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"簡","JNO":"2558","JDATE":"20220803","JTITLE":"詐欺"}